text.section:
Except as otherwise provided in subsection (d), a description of collateral reasonably identifies the collateral if it identifies the collateral by:
Specific listing;
Category;
Except as otherwise provided in subsection (e), a type of collateral defined in Titles 1 through 10 of this article;
Quantity;
Computational or allocational formula or procedure; or
Except as otherwise provided in subsection (c), any other method, if the identity of the collateral is objectively determinable.
